  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-md w-full font-normal">
  On-Chain News is committed to providing our readers with accurate, fair, and unbiased coverage of the world of digital currencies. 
      
   To achieve this goal, we have established the following news policy:
     <div class="divider my-0"></div>
  
  <ul list class="list-decimal" "list-outside">
  <li>Accuracy: We strive to ensure that all of the information we publish is accurate and based on reliable sources. If we discover that any information we have published is incorrect, we will promptly issue a correction.</li>

   <div class="divider my-0"></div>
 
   <li>Fairness: We strive to present all sides of a story and to give equal weight to differing viewpoints. We will not allow our personal opinions or biases to influence the content we publish.</li>

   <div class="divider my-0"></div>

  <li>Unbiased: We will not allow commercial or financial interests to influence the content we publish. We will disclose any conflicts of interest that may arise.</li>
     
   <div class="divider my-0"></div>

  <li>Transparency: We will be transparent about our sources and will clearly label any content that is opinion or analysis rather than news.</li>

   <div class="divider my-0"></div>

    <li>Confidentiality: We will respect the confidentiality of our sources and will not disclose their identities unless it's a legal situation or we are required to do so by law.</li>
 </ul>
     
    <div class="divider my-0"></div>

  We are committed to upholding these principles in all of our coverage and welcome feedback from our readers if you feel we are not upholding these standards.    
